    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior has visible scratches and minor dents, and the interior shows signs of wear including faded upholstery and light scuffs on the trim. The engine runs adequately but is not without age-related wear. Suitable for a buyer looking for a functional vehicle at a budget-friendly price.",
      "price": 18000.0,
